Description: Implements an efficient cross-validated approach to covariance
  matrix estimation in high-dimensional settings. The procedure data adaptively
  identifies the optimal estimator of the covariance matrix from a set of
  pre-specified candidates. Diagnostic tools are also provided for assessing
  the quality of the selected covariance matrix estimator.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
